cdata.name: VV Coin
cdata.desc:
VVCoin team aims to create a mobile application that will use Augmented Reality to link tourists along with merchants, service providers and other tourists;
thus bringing the tourists closer and bringing them into a community.

VVCoin mission is to facilitate tourists, traveler and the businesses associated with tourism sector. By offering VVCoin, the team aims to ensure that 
tourists avoid the transactional costs and the time taking process associated with money conversion.
